# Integrity International Academy - Design System Rules

## Design Principles
- Maintain consistency across all components, pages, and interactions
- Follow mobile-first responsive design approach
- Ensure accessibility (WCAG AA standards minimum)
- Prioritize clean, modern, and professional aesthetics

## Color Palette (MUST USE THESE EXACT VALUES)

### Primary Colors
- Primary Teal: #008080 (--color-primary)
  - Use for: Main buttons, primary CTAs, active states, brand accents
  - Hover: #047474 or #046a6a
- Secondary Coral: #FF6F61 (--color-secondary)
  - Use for: Secondary buttons, accent elements, highlights
- Text/Dark Slate: #2F4F4F (--color-text)
  - Use for: Body text, headings, icons

### Neutral Colors
- Background: #ffffff (--color-bg)
- Muted Text: #64748b
- Border: #e2e8f0 (--color-border)
- Surface: #f8fafc (--color-surface)

### Status Colors
- Success: #16a34a
- Warning: #d97706
- Danger: #dc2626

## Typography System

### Font Family
- Primary: 'Roboto', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif
- Always use var(--font-family-sans) in CSS

### Font Sizes (from theme.css variables)
- H1: 32px (--font-size-h1)
- H2: 28px (--font-size-h2)
- H3: 24px (--font-size-h3)
- H4: 20px (--font-size-h4)
- H5: 18px (--font-size-h5)
- H6: 16px (--font-size-h6)
- Body: 16px (--font-size-body)

### Font Weights
- Regular: 400 (--font-weight-regular)
- Medium: 500 (--font-weight-medium)
- Bold: 700 (--font-weight-bold)

### Line Height
- Default: 1.5 (--line-height)
- Headings: Use tighter spacing when appropriate

## Spacing System (4px baseline)

Use these exact spacing values from theme.css:
- --space-1: 4px
- --space-2: 8px
- --space-3: 12px
- --space-4: 16px
- --space-5: 20px
- --space-6: 24px
- --space-7: 28px
- --space-8: 32px

### Tailwind Spacing Guidelines
- Use consistent Tailwind spacing classes: p-4, m-6, gap-4, etc.
- Maintain consistent margins between sections: mb-12 or mb-16
- Use px-4 for container padding, px-6 for larger screens if needed

## Border Radius

Use theme variables:
- Small: 4px (--radius-sm)
- Medium: 8px (--radius-md)
- Large: 12px (--radius-lg)

Default button radius: 8px (rounded)
Default card radius: 8px (rounded)

## Component Standards

### Buttons
- Primary: Teal background (#008080), white text, rounded-md, px-5 py-3
- Secondary: Border with teal color, transparent background, hover:bg-teal-50
- Use consistent sizing: px-5 py-3 for standard buttons
- Hover states: Always transition smoothly (transition-colors)

### Cards
- Background: white
- Border: 1px solid var(--color-border)
- Border-radius: var(--radius-md) (8px)
- Shadow: var(--shadow-sm)
- Padding: p-6 standard, adjust for content
- Hover: Add shadow-md on hover

### Images
- Always include alt text
- Use loading="lazy" except for hero/first image
- Hero images: h-[52vh] md:h-[70vh]
- Gallery images: aspect-[4/3] for consistency
- Object-fit: cover for hero, cover or contain as appropriate

### Forms
- Input fields: border rounded, px-3 py-2
- Labels: block text-sm font-medium mb-1
- Validation: Real-time with clear error messages
- Focus states: Use var(--focus-ring) - 3px teal outline

### Navigation
- Header height: py-3
- Logo height: h-10 (40px)
- Nav links: gap-6 spacing
- Active state: text-teal-700 font-medium
- Hover state: hover:text-teal-700
- Mobile menu: Off-canvas with smooth transitions

### Footer
- Border-top: border-t border-slate-200
- Padding: py-8
- Text size: text-sm
- Grid layout: md:grid-cols-3

## Layout Standards

### Container Width
- Max width: max-w-7xl mx-auto
- Padding: px-4 (mobile), px-6 (desktop optional)
- Section spacing: py-12 or py-16

### Grid System
- Use Tailwind grid: grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3
- Gap: gap-4 (small), gap-6 (medium), gap-8 (large)

## Slider/Carousel Standards

### Hero Slider
- Height: h-[52vh] md:h-[70vh]
- Transition: 1000ms (1 second)
- Autoplay: 5000ms (5 seconds)
- Effect: Fade with crossFade
- Captions: Positioned at bottom with teal gradient overlay

### Navigation Controls
- Arrow buttons: 44px × 44px (desktop), 36px × 36px (mobile)
- Background: rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.7) with backdrop blur
- Hover: Full teal (#008080) with scale(1.15)

### Pagination Dots
- Size: 12px × 12px (desktop), 10px × 10px (mobile)
- Inactive: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) with border
- Active: Teal (#008080) with scale(1.3) and glow

## Accessibility Requirements

### Must Include
- Skip to content link (sr-only, focus:not-sr-only)
- Semantic HTML5 elements
- ARIA labels where appropriate
- Keyboard navigation support
- Focus visible states on all interactive elements
- Alt text on all images
- Color contrast: Minimum 4.5:1 for normal text

### Focus States
- Use: box-shadow: var(--focus-ring)
- Focus ring: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,128,128,0.35)
- Border-radius: var(--radius-sm)

## Code Organization

### CSS
- All theme variables in assets/css/theme.css
- Use CSS variables (--color-*, --font-*, --space-*, etc.)
- Inline styles only for dynamic values
- Component-specific styles in theme.css with clear comments

### JavaScript
- All site-wide scripts in assets/js/main.js
- Use IIFE pattern: (function() { ... })();
- Mobile menu toggle functionality
- Slider initialization with proper error handling

### HTML Structure
- Consistent header/footer across all pages
- Semantic markup: <header>, <nav>, <main>, <footer>, <section>
- Consistent class naming with Tailwind utilities
- Logo path: assets/icons/logo.jpg

## File Naming Conventions

### Images
- Hero: hero-{number}-{description}.jpg
- Gallery: gallery-{category}-{number}.jpg
- Leadership: {role}.jpg
- Facilities: {facility-name}.jpg
- Use lowercase with hyphens, no spaces

### HTML Files
- Use kebab-case: about.html, manager-message.html
- Academics: academics-{level}.html

## Performance Standards

### Images
- Optimize to 70% JPEG quality for web
- Max dimensions: 1920px width for hero, 1280px for gallery, 800px for portraits
- Use loading="lazy" except first/hero images
- Include decoding="async"

### JavaScript
- Load external libraries from CDN with integrity checks
- Defer non-critical scripts
- Use event delegation where possible

## Responsive Breakpoints

- Mobile: < 768px
- Tablet: 768px - 1024px
- Desktop: > 1024px

### Common Patterns
- Hide/show: hidden md:block
- Grid columns: grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3
- Text sizes: text-sm md:text-base
- Padding: px-4 md:px-6
- Spacing: mb-6 md:mb-12

## Animation & Transitions

### Transition Timing
- Default: 0.3s ease
- Smooth: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)
- Slider: 1s (1000ms) cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)

### Hover Effects
- Buttons: transition-colors, slight scale on icons
- Cards: Add shadow, no transform unless specified
- Links: Color change only, no underline

## Prohibited Practices

- DO NOT use inline styles for static styling (use classes)
- DO NOT create new colors outside the palette without approval
- DO NOT use arbitrary spacing values (use theme variables or Tailwind scale)
- DO NOT skip alt text on images
- DO NOT use font sizes outside the defined scale
- DO NOT mix different border radius values randomly
- DO NOT create components without considering mobile responsiveness

## Required Consistency Checks

Before implementing any new component or page:
1. Does it use the correct color palette?
2. Are spacing values from the theme system?
3. Is it responsive (mobile-first)?
4. Are accessibility standards met?
5. Does it match existing component styles?
6. Are transitions/animations consistent?
7. Is the typography scale respected?

---

## Quick Reference

**Primary Color**: #008080 (Teal)
**Secondary Color**: #FF6F61 (Coral)  
**Text Color**: #2F4F4F (Dark Slate)
**Font**: Roboto
**Base Spacing**: 4px increments
**Border Radius**: 4px (sm), 8px (md), 12px (lg)
**Button Padding**: px-5 py-3
**Container Max Width**: max-w-7xl
**Section Padding**: py-12 or py-16

